    "feat": {
        "name": "Agent of All Holds",
        "type": "stat_block_section",
        "subtype": "feat",
        "text": "Orcs across Belkzen recognize you as an honored lorekeeper. You\u2019re adept at leveraging this status and showing off your tattoos to resolve conflicts, change minds, or distract others from a faux pas. You get a failure on the check, rather than a critical failure. If the triggering check was made against a creature with the orc trait, you can instead add the fortune trait to this ability and reroll the check, treating any critical failure as a failure.",
